thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Mary, Joe & Angelo

author: Mary, Joe & Angelo
title: Mary, Joe & Angelo
text:
We chose Michelle and her team to sell our family home and we couldn't be happier.
She kept us informed throughout the campaign, her knowledge of the local market and her experience were all contributing factors on a great result.
We have no hesitation in recommending Michelle and the team at Nelson Alexander for a truly professional experience.
